The Czech economy grew up in this year's third quarter by 1,5% compared to the previous year.
Compared to the Vorquartal stagnated gross domestic product, and, according to Tsch. Statistical office confirmed the trend of the slowdown of economic performance.
The results are worse than the forecasts of analysts.
