Some people are even of the opinion that your concert will be the biggest show of the year.
This is not a little bit of pressure from your visit?
Some of the greatest shows that we have made in the last 21 years, took place in the last two weeks.
We have played a few giant shows in Sao Paulo, and we hope that we are prepared for this concert in Costa Rica.
Indeed, we have to play there.
We love this country, we like to surf and are enthusiastic about the jungle for Costa Rica is one of the best countries in the world.
How did your Costa Rica and its waves for surfing?
