The Queen said that it will be that by the end of the year 2015, 175 million poor families have access to these financial services and that 10 million of these households will exceed the poverty line.
The concept of micro-credit in Spain and the rest of the world Muhammad Yunus, "a few years ago initiated way back" to the Queen Sofia as a "act of justice and recognition."
